member.remarks:
Implement this interface for each schema version transition so that old JSONL files remain readable as the domain model evolves, without requiring bulk data migration.
Registration pattern:
// Register in DI: services.AddSingleton<ISchemaUpcaster<Trade>>, TradeV1ToCurrentUpcaster>();
Convention: the implementing class name should follow the pattern {DomainType}V{FromVersion}ToCurrentUpcaster so it is self-documenting.
